       Name: Cloak:absorption
       Kind: Spell
     Target: TAR_CHAR_DEFENSIVE
   Position: POS_STANDING
   Min Mana: 500
 Wait Beats: 12
 Can Learn: FALSE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: @@NThe @@lcloak@@N around your body fades.
Acquisition:
   - Not learnable by player classes.
Description:
   Cloak:absorption surrounds the caster in a shimmering cloak that has a
   chance to absorb offensive spells cast against them. When a spell hits the
   caster, there is a (pseudo_level - 55) percent chance that the cloak will
   absorb the spell entirely, negating its damage.

   When a spell is absorbed, the mana cost of that spell is restored to the
   caster's mana pool (up to their maximum mana), effectively turning enemy
   spells into fuel.

   The cloak only triggers against offensive targeted spells (TAR_CHAR_OFFENSIVE).

   Duration scales with pseudo-level (pseudo_level / 8 rounds).
*******************************************************************************
